854
01:01:37,730 --> 01:01:39,756
-That's it?
-<i>On him.</i>

855
01:01:39,933 --> 01:01:43,803
<i>Richard Thomas Straker,</i>
<i>born in Tampa, Florida.</i>

856
01:01:43,973 --> 01:01:49,380
<i>E</i>x<i>pelled from UF in 1 966</i>
<i>for selling MDMA.</i>

