859
01:01:59,495 --> 01:02:01,589
Thanks, Nolly.

860
01:02:02,500 --> 01:02:04,833
-Y<i>our daughter called from Florida.</i>
-Danny!

861
01:02:05,004 --> 01:02:06,529
<i>Congratulations, boss.</i>

862
01:02:06,706 --> 01:02:10,165
-Stop this nonsense.
