don't make house calls anymore.

874
01:02:50,970 --> 01:02:53,770
-He says they're on a pedestal.
-l didn't say that.

875
01:02:53,942 --> 01:02:57,811
Well, l wouldn't say a pedestal,
but l guess l could make a house call.

876
01:03:16,508 --> 01:03:17,806
Ruth?

877
01:03:27,290 --> 01:03:29,088
Ruth.

878
01:03:29,327 --> 01:03:32,264
lt's freezing in here.

879
01:03:32,866 --> 01:03:35,358
l came home from school.

880
01:03:36,036 --> 01:03:38,301
What's wrong, honey?

881
01:03:38,641 --> 01:03:40,575
Are you sick?

882
01:03:47,821 --> 01:03:50,313
Why don't you let me
take that necklace off?

883
01:03:50,491 --> 01:03:51,982
No.

884
01:03:53,663 --> 01:03:56,633
l had the strangest dream.

885
01:03:57,134 --> 01:03:59,797
