907
01:06:31,060 --> 01:06:33,154
Stop staring at me.

908
01:06:35,066 --> 01:06:36,557
Damn you.

909
01:06:36,735 --> 01:06:39,227
You will shut those eyes!

910
01:06:39,406 --> 01:06:41,534
Damn you, shut those eyes!

