may be selling pot on the bus.

916
01:07:09,683 --> 01:07:12,711
-That's bull.
-ls he crazy? My God.

917
01:07:12,888 --> 01:07:15,380
What's the problem
between you and Charlie?

918
01:07:15,559 --> 01:07:19,292
What, besides the fact l don't
have a father to kick his ass?

919
01:07:20,966 --> 01:07:23,835
Maybe l can speak to the principal
at Mark's school.

920
01:07:24,004 --> 01:07:25,802
Maybe she can broker a truce.

921
01:07:26,007 --> 01:07:30,912
You know what? Don't bother. The guy's
a moo-goo-gai maniac anyway.

922
01:07:31,248 --> 01:07:32,716
What?

923
01:07:33,785 --> 01:07:36,585
You know, like, Vietnam, the....

924
01:07:36,757 --> 01:07:39,852
Charlie was there.
He shows us pictures on the bus.

925
01:07:40,027 --> 01:07:42,519
He thinks he can, like,
impress us or something.

926
01:07:42,699 --> 01:07:44,998
Don't lie about this, Mark.

927
01:07:45,169 --> 01:07:47,934
He keeps them locked
in his glove compartment.

928
01:07:57,052 --> 01:07:58,748
Royce!

929
01:07:58,955 --> 01:08:00,719
Royce, no!

930
01:08:01,592 --> 01:08:04,358
You're going to die.
Are you ready to die, doctor?

931
01:08:04,531 --> 01:08:07,865
ls my wife a whore?
lf not, you think you can pump her for free?

932
01:08:08,035 --> 01:08:10,197
-No, no.
-No, because she is a whore.

933
01:08:10,706 --> 01:08:14,370
-Royce, baby, please--
-Shut up, Sandy. Shut the hell up!

934
01:08:15,880 --> 01:08:19,841
That's a $ 1 0,000 whore you just
rolled off. You understand?

935
01:08:20,086 --> 01:08:23,056
Ten thousand tomorrow,
