940
01:08:56,673 --> 01:08:58,733
-Here you go.
-Thank you.

941
01:09:02,749 --> 01:09:07,188
-Hi, guys. What can l get you?
-Hey, Susie, take a seat.

942
01:09:07,356 --> 01:09:09,018
l'm pretty busy now, Floyd.

943
01:09:13,064 --> 01:09:15,192
Hi, Mike. How are you?

944
01:09:15,835 --> 01:09:20,536
-Well, l'm fine, Susan. Thanks for asking.
-So where you been, Susie?

945
01:09:21,944 --> 01:09:23,469
Working.

946
01:09:24,447 --> 01:09:27,144
Can we talk about this
another time? Soon?

947
01:09:27,351 --> 01:09:30,049
-l think we have some things to talk about.
-We do.

948
01:09:30,223 --> 01:09:33,921
oh, that was good, Floyd,
but l think we can push a bit further.

949
01:09:34,229 --> 01:09:38,361
My point being is, why doesn't anyone
here just, l don't know, say the truth?

950
01:09:39,002 --> 01:09:40,333
What's wrong with you?

951
01:09:40,505 --> 01:09:42,701
-He doesn't feel well.
-Come on, Floyd.

952
01:09:42,875 --> 01:09:44,137
Tell her you're pissed.

953
01:09:44,343 --> 01:09:46,073
