957
01:09:53,991 --> 01:09:56,119
At least say something real.

958
01:09:57,930 --> 01:10:00,024
Look, this-- This isn't fair, Susie.

959
01:10:00,767 --> 01:10:02,531
Are you with me or with him?

960
01:10:02,837 --> 01:10:05,864
-Neither.
